    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of small West Indian tree native to Central America and the Caribbean islands. It is a slow-growing tree that has brittle, black heartwood.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
